<subSubSection id="C5BCF8D23209FFF15CF7056DFECDF9EC" pageId="7" pageNumber="408" type="description">
<paragraph id="8D19AB593209FFF15CF7056DFEBFFA4C" blockId="7.[174,1232,1299,1582]" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">
D i s t r i b u t i o n. From southern Fennoscandia southwards to Iberian Peninsula; from 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15CE5054AFEB2FA8F" box="[241,326,1331,1357]" name="Ireland" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Ireland</collectingCountry>
eastwards through Central and Southern Europe (
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15FB1054AFC2AFA8F" box="[933,990,1331,1357]" name="Italy" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Italy</collectingCountry>
, former 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15852054AFB3DFA8C" box="[1094,1225,1331,1358]" name="Serbia" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Yugoslavia</collectingCountry>
) into 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15CF7052AFEBCFAAF" box="[227,328,1363,1389]" name="Bulgaria" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Bulgaria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15D46052AFE53FAAF" box="[338,423,1363,1389]" name="Turkey" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Turkey</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF15DCB052AFDDFFAAF" box="[479,555,1363,1389]" name="Russia" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Russia</collectingCountry>
as far as western Siberia. Also in N Africa (
<collectingCountry id="F5B1EBC93209FFF1580F052AFB78FAAC" box="[1051,1164,1363,1390]" name="Morocco" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Morocco</collectingCountry>
); 
